19
00:00:18,564 --> 00:00:20,733
<i>Ahsoka Tano on the run!</i>

20
00:00:20,775 --> 00:00:22,777
<i>After an attack on the Jedi Temple,</i>

21
00:00:22,818 --> 00:00:26,072
<i>Anakin Skywalker's young Padawan
found herself accused</i>

22
00:00:26,155 --> 00:00:28,574
<i>of murdering the person
responsible for the bombings.</i>

23
00:00:29,408 --> 00:00:30,785
<i>With no choice but to run,</i>

24
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:34,288
<i>she was chased by her master,
who begged her to turn herself in.</i>

25
00:00:35,581 --> 00:00:38,960
<i>Knowing there is little hope
of being cleared of the crimes,</i>

26
00:00:39,085 --> 00:00:44,298
<i>Ahsoka decided to find out the truth
and prove her innocence on her own.</i>

27
00:00:48,761 --> 00:00:50,346
<i>After further investigation,</i>

28
00:00:50,471 --> 00:00:53,641
<i>there can be little doubt that
the clone officers murdered in the escape</i>

29
00:00:53,766 --> 00:00:56,269
<i>were killed by none other
than Ahsoka Tano herself.</i>

30
00:00:56,769 --> 00:00:59,772
<i>She used a Jedi mind-trick to convince
the clone to open the door,</i>

31
00:00:59,814 --> 00:01:04,318
<i>and then proceeded to cut him down,
along with five other clones along the way.</i>

32
00:01:05,194 --> 00:01:09,824
I do not believe that Ahsoka
could have fallen so far.

33
00:01:10,032 --> 00:01:12,952
<i>The beliefs of the Jedi Council
are irrelevant.</i>

34
00:01:12,994 --> 00:01:15,371
<i>We deal strictly in facts and evidence,</i>

35
00:01:15,496 --> 00:01:19,667
<i>and the evidence points to Padawan Tano
being guilty of the attack on the Temple</i>

36
00:01:20,001 --> 00:01:21,669
<i>and the murder of the Republic officers.</i>

37
00:01:22,169 --> 00:01:23,671
<i>This is sedition.</i>

38
00:01:27,341 --> 00:01:32,138
Skywalker, was there no way
to stop your Padawan before she escaped?

39
00:01:32,888 --> 00:01:34,724
No, Master Mundi.

40
00:01:34,849 --> 00:01:38,853
The Council believes that Ahsoka
may be guilty of the crime.

41
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:41,397
Still believe they are wrong, do you? Hmm?

42
00:01:41,522 --> 00:01:44,025
I believe she didn't kill the clone troopers

43
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:47,028
or the woman who used the nano-droids
to blow up the Temple.

44
00:01:47,069 --> 00:01:50,323
That's why she's running.
To prove her innocence.

45
00:01:50,865 --> 00:01:55,828
Now she's in the lower depths.
With her skills, she will be hard to find.

46
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,830
Two teams we will send.

47
00:01:57,872 --> 00:02:02,752
Master Skywalker and Master Plo Koon,
with clones you will go.

48
00:02:03,085 --> 00:02:06,881
I think it would be best
if Skywalker stayed here.

49
00:02:07,089 --> 00:02:10,384
Having you involved may actually
make things worse.

50
00:02:11,636 --> 00:02:16,599
Master Windu, with all due respect,
she is my Padawan.

51
00:02:17,308 --> 00:02:19,727
The reason for you not to go.

52
00:02:19,769 --> 00:02:23,314
<i>I think we're being foolish
if we take Anakin off this mission.</i>

53
00:02:23,397 --> 00:02:24,607
<i>Who knows her better?</i>

54
00:02:24,732 --> 00:02:26,233
He's emotionally tied to her.

55
00:02:26,317 --> 00:02:29,070
Probably too emotional
to do what needs to be done.

56
00:02:29,153 --> 00:02:33,157
I'd rather capture Ahsoka and find out
the truth than let her run because of a lie.

57
00:02:33,574 --> 00:02:37,953
You must prove to us that you will
stay focused, can you?

58
00:02:38,412 --> 00:02:40,665
I've already alerted
security on the lower levels

59
00:02:40,748 --> 00:02:42,333
to be on the lookout for Ahsoka.

60
00:02:44,418 --> 00:02:48,422
Go swiftly then, Skywalker,
and bring back this lost child

61
00:02:48,756 --> 00:02:50,800
before it is too late.

62
00:02:51,801 --> 00:02:53,094
Yes, Master.

63
00:03:28,379 --> 00:03:30,297
This one just came in.

64
00:03:30,631 --> 00:03:33,634
Looks like the Jedi are after one
of their own.

65
00:03:33,718 --> 00:03:35,886
She's armed and dangerous. Alert all units.

66
00:03:38,055 --> 00:03:39,181
You heard him.

67
00:03:57,533 --> 00:03:59,326
Barriss, it's Ahsoka.

68
00:03:59,368 --> 00:04:01,829
Ahsoka, I'm so glad you're safe.

69
00:04:01,871 --> 00:04:03,998
Safe, but on the run.

70
00:04:04,081 --> 00:04:05,332
<i>Where?</i>

71
00:04:05,374 --> 00:04:08,836
I can't tell you, but someone
is definitely trying to frame me.

72
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:12,047
It's not safe for you to call me using
the Jedi communicator.

73
00:04:12,173 --> 00:04:13,883
Find another way to contact me.

74
00:04:14,008 --> 00:04:15,176
I will.

75
00:04:15,259 --> 00:04:16,844
<i>In the meantime, I'll do some digging</i>

76
00:04:16,927 --> 00:04:19,722
<i>and see if I can find anything out
to help you on my end.</i>

77
00:04:19,847 --> 00:04:20,848
Thank you, Barriss.

78
00:04:20,931 --> 00:04:22,224
<i>Be safe.</i>

79
00:04:34,069 --> 00:04:36,030
Hey, buddy, are you hungry?

80
00:04:36,572 --> 00:04:38,032
Yeah.

81
00:04:38,866 --> 00:04:40,034
Let's make a trade.

82
00:04:43,871 --> 00:04:45,206
What do you want?

83
00:04:46,332 --> 00:04:47,792
Your cloak.

84
00:05:27,665 --> 00:05:30,709
Passes, please. Passes, please.

85
00:05:35,297 --> 00:05:37,299
Passes, please.

86
00:05:47,309 --> 00:05:48,519
That's her! The rogue Jedi!

87
00:05:54,733 --> 00:05:57,570
All units respond.
We have located the rogue Jedi.

88
00:06:07,371 --> 00:06:08,414
Stop her!

89
00:06:09,248 --> 00:06:11,125
I've got her!

90
00:06:33,898 --> 00:06:35,107
Sir, look!

91
00:06:37,818 --> 00:06:38,903
Stop!

92
00:06:49,288 --> 00:06:50,456
Not good.

93
00:06:57,004 --> 00:06:59,882
Don't worry, little guy. I'll get us out of this.

94
00:07:02,843 --> 00:07:06,889
I'll think of something.
Maybe I can cut a hole in the roof.

95
00:07:11,644 --> 00:07:12,895
Almost there.

96
00:07:13,062 --> 00:07:15,022
Almost... Got it!

97
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:26,909
I, uh, guess I'm not exactly
on my game these days.

98
00:07:38,545 --> 00:07:40,547
Thanks, kid. I owe you one.

99
00:08:04,321 --> 00:08:07,032
The lower level police claim
to have spotted Commander Tano

100
00:08:07,116 --> 00:08:08,909
heading to level 1312.

101
00:08:08,993 --> 00:08:10,786
All right, let's bring her home.

102
00:08:46,405 --> 00:08:52,369
Well, well. I didn't believe it when
I first heard it, but I guess it's true.

103
00:08:52,453 --> 00:08:55,956
The Senate has put a bounty
on your horned little head.

104
00:08:58,167 --> 00:09:00,836
And I'm going to be the one who collects.

105
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:03,213
Ventress! It was you, wasn't it?

106
00:09:04,423 --> 00:09:06,925
You were behind all of this
and you framed me!

107
00:09:08,135 --> 00:09:10,471
I don't know what you're talking about.

108
00:09:10,554 --> 00:09:12,806
Yes, you do!

109
00:09:13,766 --> 00:09:17,061
So, what are you now? A bounty hunter?

110
00:09:17,478 --> 00:09:21,231
Yes. And someone who knows how
to make easy money.

111
00:09:31,909 --> 00:09:33,786
You think you're just going
to hand me over,

112
00:09:33,827 --> 00:09:36,830
and then what? Get a pat on the shoulder?

113
00:09:36,914 --> 00:09:39,166
You're a Separatist war criminal and a Sith.

114
00:09:39,249 --> 00:09:41,919
They'll have us both in prison
before you've said your name.

115
00:09:42,002 --> 00:09:44,421
I don't have to hand you over to the Jedi.

116
00:09:44,505 --> 00:09:47,758
I can hand you over to the bondsmen
and still get paid.

117
00:09:47,841 --> 00:09:51,595
I'm going to get my money,
whether you're dead or alive.

118
00:09:51,762 --> 00:09:56,517
Good luck.
Despite what you hear, I'm still a Jedi.

119
00:09:56,600 --> 00:10:00,521
I'm afraid the other Jedi
no longer see it that way.

120
00:10:01,063 --> 00:10:04,024
I hate to admit it, but you're right.

121
00:10:04,566 --> 00:10:06,902
That's why I'm going to need your help.

122
00:10:07,569 --> 00:10:11,740
In what star system do you think
I would ever help you?

123
00:10:12,574 --> 00:10:15,035
A traitorous Jedi tried
to blow up the Jedi Temple

124
00:10:15,077 --> 00:10:17,746
and has framed me for that
and other killings.

125
00:10:17,871 --> 00:10:21,542
Hmm. So, the Jedi aren't that holy after all.

126
00:10:22,042 --> 00:10:26,880
I know Dooku tried to have you killed.
I know he betrayed you.

127
00:10:27,214 --> 00:10:28,757
What if this is his new apprentice?

128
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:32,886
I've fallen from my path,
just as you've fallen from yours.

129
00:10:33,011 --> 00:10:35,389
We have a lot more in common
than you think.

130
00:10:35,889 --> 00:10:38,934
What can you offer me
that's better than money?

131
00:10:40,018 --> 00:10:41,562
If you help me,

132
00:10:41,603 --> 00:10:44,773
I'll speak to the Council and the Senate
on your behalf.

133
00:10:44,898 --> 00:10:47,568
I'll get you a full pardon for your crimes.

134
00:10:47,693 --> 00:10:52,030
You have my attention.
But I'm going to go where the tide flows.

135
00:10:53,365 --> 00:10:55,909
If the tide is flowing against you,

136
00:10:55,951 --> 00:10:59,079
don't think I'll forget about
the bounty on your head.

137
00:11:00,247 --> 00:11:01,415
Fair enough.

138
00:11:02,541 --> 00:11:04,710
I suggest we find somewhere else
to discuss this.

139
00:11:07,546 --> 00:11:08,964
Shine the light over there.

140
00:11:10,549 --> 00:11:11,925
<i>Stay where you are!</i>

141
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,615
Ventress.

142
00:11:36,909 --> 00:11:39,578
Send out the probes.
I want them found now!

143
00:11:49,588 --> 00:11:51,590
Nice place you have here.

144
00:11:51,632 --> 00:11:56,595
Not everyone on Coruscant lives
in a luxurious temple on the surface.

145
00:11:56,970 --> 00:11:59,264
I guess I'll have to get used to that.

146
00:11:59,306 --> 00:12:01,099
Just make the call.

147
00:12:09,650 --> 00:12:11,985
Adding another criminal act to your record?

148
00:12:12,152 --> 00:12:14,655
I don't want them to be able to trace it.

149
00:12:14,988 --> 00:12:17,407
Barriss, it's me.

150
00:12:19,451 --> 00:12:22,246
<i>It's so good to see you, Ahsoka.
Are you okay?</i>

151
00:12:22,329 --> 00:12:23,789
Yeah, I'm okay,

152
00:12:23,830 --> 00:12:27,584
if you consider Anakin and 100 clones
on my tail a good space to be in.

153
00:12:27,668 --> 00:12:28,919
<i>You were almost captured?</i>

154
00:12:29,002 --> 00:12:30,128
Once or twice, yeah.

155
00:12:30,504 --> 00:12:31,505
<i>Where are you?</i>

156
00:12:32,130 --> 00:12:33,924
I can't say, Barriss.

157
00:12:34,007 --> 00:12:35,842
<i>I believe I've found a clue.</i>

158
00:12:36,009 --> 00:12:38,887
A clue? How? From where?

159
00:12:38,971 --> 00:12:40,138
<i>We don't have much time, Ahsoka.</i>

160
00:12:42,808 --> 00:12:45,560
<i>Fine, I'm on level 1312.</i>

161
00:12:49,773 --> 00:12:53,151
A holobooth at the corner
of 12th and G. Got it.

162
00:12:53,485 --> 00:12:56,321
<i>Three levels up, there seems
to be an abandoned warehouse</i>

163
00:12:56,405 --> 00:12:58,490
<i>where they used to build munitions
that Letta visited</i>

164
00:12:58,657 --> 00:13:01,243
<i>during the time she was getting access
to the nano-droids.</i>

165
00:13:01,326 --> 00:13:02,703
How did you find this out?

166
00:13:03,161 --> 00:13:05,080
<i>I told you I would do some checking.</i>

167
00:13:05,163 --> 00:13:07,165
Oh, thank you, Barriss.

168
00:13:07,541 --> 00:13:09,293
<i>Be careful, Ahsoka.</i>

169
00:13:14,506 --> 00:13:15,549
Well?

170
00:13:16,508 --> 00:13:18,093
I think I have a lead.

171
00:13:25,350 --> 00:13:27,519
It doesn't seem like you need my help.

172
00:13:27,686 --> 00:13:28,895
That's not true.

173
00:13:28,979 --> 00:13:32,482
We need to find an abandoned
munitions warehouse on level 1315.

174
00:13:32,566 --> 00:13:35,152
We should be able to find
some information there.

175
00:13:37,738 --> 00:13:40,907
You know the place I'm talking about,
don't you?

176
00:13:41,074 --> 00:13:43,577
Yes, I can get you there.

177
00:13:50,792 --> 00:13:53,879
Listen to me. I don't want to fight.

178
00:13:55,714 --> 00:13:56,840
I do.

179
00:13:57,132 --> 00:13:58,967
We're taking you in now, Commander.

180
00:13:59,217 --> 00:14:02,304
That's not gonna happen, trust me.

181
00:14:02,721 --> 00:14:05,140
Now, I'm not going to hurt any of you...

182
00:14:05,223 --> 00:14:08,226
We're not going to hurt any of you,

183
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:10,771
but you're not taking me in.

184
00:14:12,564 --> 00:14:15,192
Commander, we are taking you in.

185
00:14:16,568 --> 00:14:17,694
Let's play.

186
00:14:17,778 --> 00:14:18,820
Take them out!

187
00:14:20,072 --> 00:14:21,406
Ventress, don't!

188
00:14:23,617 --> 00:14:24,826
Look out!

189
00:14:56,149 --> 00:14:57,567
See?

190
00:14:57,651 --> 00:14:59,486
Didn't kill one.

191
00:14:59,986 --> 00:15:01,571
It's the new me.

192
00:15:05,492 --> 00:15:08,370
General Plo Koon,
we had Commander Tano

193
00:15:08,495 --> 00:15:11,581
but she escaped with the help
of Asajj Ventress.

194
00:15:19,089 --> 00:15:20,507
There it is.

195
00:15:20,674 --> 00:15:23,760
That's where you're supposed
to find this clue.

196
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:36,022
I've done my part of the bargain

197
00:15:36,106 --> 00:15:38,442
which means you're on your own
from here.

198
00:15:38,525 --> 00:15:42,404
But, don't forget you have
to speak on my behalf now.

199
00:15:42,529 --> 00:15:44,573
-That was the deal.
-Agreed.

200
00:15:45,365 --> 00:15:48,201
Thanks for getting me this far at least.

201
00:15:48,368 --> 00:15:50,036
I have to admit,

202
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:54,875
I never saw us doing
anything together ever.

203
00:15:55,542 --> 00:15:57,836
These are strange times.

204
00:16:26,907 --> 00:16:30,076
I thought we decided we were going
to part ways?

205
00:16:44,424 --> 00:16:45,634
Ah!

206
00:17:20,126 --> 00:17:22,295
How am I supposed to find a clue

207
00:17:22,337 --> 00:17:24,297
when I don't even know
what I'm looking for?

208
00:17:43,483 --> 00:17:46,695
Ventress!
I see you've had a change of heart.

209
00:18:00,875 --> 00:18:02,168
Why bring me here?

210
00:18:02,711 --> 00:18:05,088
Answer me, Ventress! Why?

211
00:19:09,986 --> 00:19:11,154
Calling all units,

212
00:19:11,237 --> 00:19:13,907
<i>suspicious activity on level 1315.</i>

213
00:20:03,832 --> 00:20:05,458
Nano-droids?

214
00:20:13,007 --> 00:20:15,135
No! Wolff e, let me explain!

215
00:20:30,942 --> 00:20:32,110
Explosives.

216
00:20:32,193 --> 00:20:36,614
These are the same types of nano-droids
that were used to blow up the Jedi Temple.

217
00:20:36,948 --> 00:20:38,867
I can't believe it.

218
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:48,501
<i>Captured, she has been?</i>

219
00:20:48,585 --> 00:20:50,336
Yes, Master Yoda.

220
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:52,046
<i>Without incident?</i>

221
00:20:52,130 --> 00:20:55,091
No. She was subdued by the clones

222
00:20:55,175 --> 00:20:58,303
and found in possession
of explosive nano-droids.

223
00:20:59,137 --> 00:21:01,931
It still doesn't explain
Ventress' involvement.

224
00:21:02,015 --> 00:21:03,558
We saw her with Ahsoka.

225
00:21:03,767 --> 00:21:06,603
<i>I think there's more going on
than we know.</i>

226
00:21:06,728 --> 00:21:09,063
By Ahsoka or against her?

227
00:21:09,981 --> 00:21:12,192
<i>That remains to be seen.</i>

228
00:21:12,275 --> 00:21:13,860
<i>We're bringing her back to the Temple.</i>

229
00:21:13,985 --> 00:21:16,613
<i>Let's just hope we can keep her here.</i>

230
00:21:16,637 --> 00:21:21,637
http://hiqve.com/

